1. The Component Hold some state should be the one Updating it.

Git
... Creat New.....

echo "# file-tree-backend" >> README.md
git init
git add README.md
git commit -m "first commit"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin git@github.com:A-Arnob/file-tree-backend.git
git push -u origin main


...Push an existing repository....

git remote add origin git@github.com:A-Arnob/file-tree-backend.git
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main

..................
git add. 
git commit -m
